author: jdonnerstag
msg: a) changed all components to use render() instead of render(MarkupStream).

c) the component is no longer responsible to forward the markupstream index after rendering, only while rendering. Which means that whatever component.getMarkup() returns is what the component renders. The parent component makes sure that the parent markup is moved forward appropriately.
